---
title: Bacon Jam Roast Chicken & Sour Cream Mash with Sautéed Greens & Almonds
description: This chicken is roasted to perfection and topped with a sweet and savoury bacon jam, for a roast experience like never before. Accompanied by a creamy mash, this dish is hard to beat!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65e95492904479aa17a25248-a1c93a9a.jpeg
